---
layout: layouts/base-finpay.njk
title: "Retirement Portfolio Management | Capital Wealth Lehi, UT"
description: "Active portfolio management designed for retirement income and long-term growth. Diversified strategies, risk management, and tax-efficient investing."
breadcrumbs:
  - { name: "Home", url: "/" }
  - { name: "Services", url: "/services/" }
  - { name: "Portfolio Management", url: "/services/portfolio-management/" }
faqSchema:
  - question: "Are you a fiduciary?"
    answer: "Yes, always. We are legally and ethically obligated to act in your best interest at all times. We don't earn commissions from product sales, and we don't have hidden incentives to recommend one investment over another."
  - question: "How do you charge for portfolio management?"
    answer: "We charge a transparent percentage of assets under management. The fee is disclosed upfront, charged quarterly, and decreases as your assets grow. No hidden costs, no commissions, no surprises."
  - question: "Can I keep my current investments?"
    answer: "It depends. We'll review what you own and determine if it fits within an appropriate retirement portfolio. Some holdings may be fine; others might need to be replaced with better, lower-cost, or more tax-efficient options."
  - question: "What is your investment philosophy?"
    answer: "We believe in diversification, low-cost investments, tax efficiency, and active risk management. We don't chase returns or try to time the market. We build portfolios designed to support your retirement income needs while protecting against major downside risk."
  - question: "How often will you rebalance my portfolio?"
    answer: "We monitor portfolios continuously and rebalance strategically based on market conditions and allocation drift. This is typically quarterly, but can be more frequent during volatile markets or when tax-loss harvesting opportunities arise."
---

<style>
/* ═══════════════════════════════════════════
   EDITORIAL SERVICE PAGE — Portfolio Management
   ═══════════════════════════════════════════ */

/* Hero */
.ep-hero {
  padding: 2rem 2rem 5rem;
  background: var(--surface-container-low);
  overflow: hidden;
  margin-top: -1rem;
}

.ep-hero-inner {
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr;
  gap: 4rem;
  align-items: center;
}

.ep-chapter-label {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--secondary);
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  display: block;
}

.ep-hero-title {
  font-family: var(--font-serif-display);
  font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 5vw, 4rem);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--primary);
  line-height: 1.08;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

.ep-hero-title-italic {
  font-family: var(--font-serif-display);
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem);
  font-weight: 400;
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--on-surface-variant);
  line-height: 1.15;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
  display: block;
}

.ep-hero-body {
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  line-height: 1.7;
  color: var(--on-surface-variant);
  max-width: 540px;
  margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
}

/* Buttons — match homepage hero-btn / hero-btn-secondary */
.ep-btn-primary {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
  border-radius: 16px;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  background: rgba(0, 56, 112, 0.85);
  backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
  border: 1px solid rgba(0, 56, 112, 0.3);
  color: white;
}

.ep-btn-primary:hover {
  background: rgba(0, 56, 112, 0.95);
  transform: translateY(-2px);
  box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 56, 112, 0.15);
}

.ep-btn-ghost {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
  border-radius: 16px;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  background: transparent;
  border: 2px solid var(--primary);
  color: var(--primary);
}

.ep-btn-ghost:hover {
  background: var(--primary);
  color: white;
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}

.ep-hero-image-wrap {
  position: relative;
}

.ep-hero-image {
  width: 100%;
  aspect-ratio: 4/5;
  object-fit: cover;
  display: block;
}

.ep-pull-quote {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: -2rem;
  left: -3rem;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
  backdrop-filter: blur(30px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(30px);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
  border-left: 4px solid var(--secondary);
  border-radius: 16px;
  padding: 2rem;
  max-width: 320px;
  box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
}

.ep-pull-quote p {
  font-family: var(--font-serif-display);
  font-style: italic;
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  line-height: 1.45;
  color: var(--primary);
  margin: 0;
}

.ep-pull-quote cite {
  display: block;
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  font-style: normal;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--on-surface-variant);
  margin-top: 1rem;
}

/* Key Facts Row */
.ep-facts {
  padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
  background: var(--surface);
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(194, 198, 210, 0.2);
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(194, 198, 210, 0.2);
}

.ep-facts-inner {
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  gap: 2rem;
}

.ep-fact {
  flex: 1;
}

.ep-fact-label {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.65rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--on-surface-variant);
  margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
}

.ep-fact-value {
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--on-surface);
}

/* Framework Section */
.ep-framework {
  padding: 6rem 2rem;
  background: var(--surface);
}

.ep-framework-inner {
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
  gap: 4rem;
}

.ep-framework-title {
  font-family: var(--font-serif-display);
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem);
  font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--primary);
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.ep-framework-accent {
  width: 3rem;
  height: 3px;
  background: var(--secondary);
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.ep-framework-desc {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  line-height: 1.8;
  color: var(--on-surface-variant);
}

.ep-framework-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 1px;
  background: rgba(194, 198, 210, 0.2);
}

.ep-framework-card {
  padding: 2.5rem;
  background: white;
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
  border-top: 3px solid transparent;
}

.ep-framework-card:hover {
  background: var(--surface-container-low);
