{# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
   7. FAQ — Editorial accordion
   ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ #}
<section class="ep-faq">
  <div class="ep-faq-inner">
    <div>
      <span class="ep-chapter-label">Common Questions</span>
      <h2 class="ep-faq-title">Portfolio Management FAQ</h2>
      <p class="ep-faq-sub">Learn about our professional investment management approach for retirement portfolios.</p>
      <a href="/contact/" class="ep-btn-ghost">Ask About Portfolio Management</a>
    </div>
    <div>
      <button class="ep-faq-item" onclick="this.classList.toggle('active')">
        <span class="ep-faq-q">Are you a fiduciary? <span class="ep-faq-icon">+</span></span>
        <div class="ep-faq-a"><p>Yes, always. We are legally and ethically obligated to act in your best interest at all times. We don't earn commissions from product sales, and we don't have hidden incentives to recommend one investment over another.</p></div>
      </button>
      <button class="ep-faq-item" onclick="this.classList.toggle('active')">
        <span class="ep-faq-q">How do you charge for portfolio management? <span class="ep-faq-icon">+</span></span>
        <div class="ep-faq-a"><p>We charge a transparent percentage of assets under management. The fee is disclosed upfront, charged quarterly, and decreases as your assets grow. No hidden costs, no commissions, no surprises.</p></div>
      </button>
      <button class="ep-faq-item" onclick="this.classList.toggle('active')">
        <span class="ep-faq-q">Can I keep my current investments? <span class="ep-faq-icon">+</span></span>
        <div class="ep-faq-a"><p>It depends. We'll review what you own and determine if it fits within an appropriate retirement portfolio. Some holdings may be fine; others might need to be replaced with better, lower-cost, or more tax-efficient options.</p></div>
      </button>
      <button class="ep-faq-item" onclick="this.classList.toggle('active')">
        <span class="ep-faq-q">What is your investment philosophy? <span class="ep-faq-icon">+</span></span>
        <div class="ep-faq-a"><p>We believe in diversification, low-cost investments, tax efficiency, and active risk management. We don't chase returns or try to time the market. We build portfolios designed to support your retirement income needs while protecting against major downside risk.</p></div>
      </button>
      <button class="ep-faq-item" onclick="this.classList.toggle('active')">
        <span class="ep-faq-q">How often will you rebalance my portfolio? <span class="ep-faq-icon">+</span></span>
        <div class="ep-faq-a"><p>We monitor portfolios continuously and rebalance strategically based on market conditions and allocation drift. This is typically quarterly, but can be more frequent during volatile markets or when tax-loss harvesting opportunities arise.</p></div>
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

